<br>
 Thank god Alzabo and Sentry invited me to this wonderful organization. Some of the stuff that comes across the board is just idle chatter. Most of what goes on is Quest/zone info &amp; Requests for assistance (ie. corpse retrieval in very hazardous zones) <br>
<br>
